Subject: Re: [T2] brake help needed!

Get a 1/2" breaker bar and the correct size socket. I think it's a 19mm 
,but not sure on the size.
It's much safer for you and the bus. Those cross shaped lug wrenches are 
junk. You can't get safe leverage and they take up a lot of room.

Bill M
Mystic,CT
78 Westy



